creator: Hubworks Interactive, LLC
descriptionHtml:
ZipSchedules is the easiest way for employees and managers to interact and communicate remotely.

ZipSchedules puts the work schedule in your pocket. Now communicating, receiving notification whenever a new schedule is published or an existing schedule is updated, requesting time-offs, swapping shifts, editing availability are just a click away.

FEATURES FOR MANAGERS:
View historical, current or future published schedules.
Control alerts and notifications.
Approve or deny availability, time off, shift offer or accept requests.
Notify employees about their schedule.
View all employee's schedules and contact information.

FEATURES FOR EMPLOYEES:
View work schedule anytime, anywhere
Request Availability.
Request partial day or all day time off(s) and keep a track of the request.
Flexibility to offer/swap shifts with other employees
View coworkers contact information depending upon their preference whether to share information or not.
Send Messages to co-workers.
descriptionShort: Simple and easy way to create manageable employee schedules for a restaurant.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
* Manager can set temporary password for employees.
* Get notified of all the notifications you have on the bell icon.
* Bug Fixes.
